---
// Component for the hero section
---
<section class="relative bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        <span class="block">サロンの成功を、</span>
        <span class="block text-orange-600">あらゆる角度から支援する。</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600">
        美容機器の選定から、最新の集客ノウハウまで。サロンオーナー様の悩みに寄り添う専門情報サイトです。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 max-w-sm mx-auto sm:max-w-none sm:flex sm:justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
        <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:inline-grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-5">
            <a href="/devices" class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
              美容機器を探す
            </a>
            <a href="/management" class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-orange-700 bg-orange-100 hover:bg-orange-200 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
              経営ノウハウを学ぶ
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <form action="/search" method="get" class="relative max-w-xl mx-auto">
          <input type="search" name="q" placeholder="お探しの機器名やキーワードを入力" class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-lg rounded-full border-2 border-gray-300 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 transition">
          <button type="submit" class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-full p-3 hover:bg-orange-700 transition">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path></svg>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
